.TH XIL\-IMPORT "1" "2026\-04\-24" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.8" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-import
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-import
[-h] (--episode EPISODE | --tag TAG) [--show SHOW] --zip ZIP_PATH [--parsed PARSED] [--stems-dir STEMS_DIR] [--dry-run] [--force] [--gen-sfx] [--gen-music] [--gen-beats] [--all]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Import ElevenLabs Studio export ZIP into pipeline stems.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,EPISODE\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S02E02) — derives parsed JSON and stems dir

.TP
\fB\-\-tag\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Raw tag for non\-episodic content (e.g. V01C03, D01)

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-zip\fR \fI\,ZIP_PATH\/\fR
Path to the ElevenLabs Studio export ZIP file

.TP
\fB\-\-parsed\fR \fI\,PARSED\/\fR
Override parsed JSON path (default: parsed/parsed_<slug>_{TAG}.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-stems\-dir\fR \fI\,STEMS_DIR\/\fR
Override stems output directory (default: stems/{TAG})

.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show extraction plan without writing files

.TP
\fB\-\-force\fR
Overwrite existing stems on disk

.TP
\fB\-\-gen\-sfx\fR
Include SFX direction entries

.TP
\fB\-\-gen\-music\fR
Include MUSIC direction entries

.TP
\fB\-\-gen\-beats\fR
Include BEAT direction entries

.TP
\fB\-\-all\fR
Include all direction types (SFX, MUSIC, BEAT, AMBIENCE)

